# Input

```scss
$lines:[full-start  ,  main-start
/  main-end,
  full-end];
$columns:[col-start] minmax(200px,  1fr
) [col-end];
 $rows:[header-start] auto [header-end
body-start] 1fr [body-end];
   .grid{


grid-template-columns:[wide-start]/[wide-end];
 grid-template-rows:[header-start] auto
  [header-end body-start] 1fr [body-end];
 grid-column:[col-start]
  /[col-end];
	}

```


# Formatted

```scss
$lines: [full-start, main-start / main-end, full-end];
$columns: [col-start] minmax(200px, 1fr) [col-end];
$rows: [header-start] auto [header-end body-start] 1fr [body-end];
.grid {
	grid-template-columns: [wide-start] / [wide-end];
	grid-template-rows: [header-start] auto [header-end body-start] 1fr [body-end];
	grid-column: [col-start] / [col-end];
}

```
